[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0872","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0596","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 日志文件大小与保留期限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 日志文件的最大大小或保留期限配置不当，可能导致日志文件无限制增长耗尽磁盘空间，引发拒绝服务；或日志过早轮转覆盖，导致关键安全事件记录丢失，影响事后审计与取证分析。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0596"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.267","remediation":"建议在 Windows NT 事件查看器中右键「事件日志」→「日志设置」，将日志最大大小根据磁盘容量设为 512MB 以上，回卷策略设为「按需要覆盖事件」而非「不要覆盖事件」。若仍使用旧版系统，应升级至 Windows Server 2003 及以上版本以获得完善的日志审计功能。作为临时缓解措施，可设置组策略定期归档并清理旧日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0596","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0596.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86256/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0871","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0871.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0594","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 可移动介质未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统未对可移动介质驱动器（如软盘驱动器、光盘驱动器）的访问权限进行适当限制，导致未经授权的本地用户可通过物理接触或网络共享途径读取受保护的可移动介质中的敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，攻击者只需能够物理访问目标系统或通过网络访问共享的可移动介质即可利用，可能造成系统配置信息、密码文件或加密密钥等机密数据泄露。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0594"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.013","remediation":"通过本地安全策略设置，为\"计算机配置→Windows 设置→安全设置→本地策略→用户权利指派\"中的\"从可移动媒体访问\"项限制为仅授权管理员；同时修改注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon 中的 AllocateCDRoms 和 AllocateFloppies 值为 1，限制非管理员用户访问可移动媒体驱动器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0594","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0594.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-788r-28g9-93jm/GHSA-788r-28g9-93jm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86242/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0871.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0870","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0593","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Winlogon 关闭系统无需登录漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 Winlogon 注册表项中 ShutdownWithoutLogon 键值默认设置为启用，允许拥有物理接触权限的未授权用户直接关闭系统而无需登录认证。该漏洞源于系统默认安全配置不当，攻击者仅需物理访问目标主机即可触发关机操作，导致系统可用性受损。影响 Windows NT 系列系统，CVSS 评分 4.9，危害等级中危。建议管理员通过注册表或组策略禁用此功能以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0593"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.887","remediation":"在注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon` 中将 `ShutdownWithoutLogon` 值设为 `0`（REG_SZ），或通过组策略「计算机配置→Windows 设置→安全设置→本地策略→安全选项」启用「关闭系统：仅允许已登录的用户使用关机权限」。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/59333","http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc722469.aspx","http://www.microsoft.com/technet/archive/winntas/deploy/confeat/06wntpcc.mspx?mfr=true","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1291","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0593","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0593.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86243/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0869","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0869.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0592","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 登录用户名信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统登录框默认会显示上一次成功登录的用户名，导致系统敏感信息泄露。本地攻击者通过物理访问目标系统即可获取有效用户名，降低了暴力破解登录密码的难度。该漏洞影响所有 Windows NT 及早期 Windows 版本，攻击者无需任何特权即可利用此漏洞收集账户信息，从而为后续攻击提供便利。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0592"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.777","remediation":"在 Windows NT 中，打开组策略编辑器 (gpedit.msc)，依次展开「计算机配置 → Windows 设置 → 安全设置 → 本地策略 → 安全选项」，将「交互式登录: 不显示上次登录的用户名」设置为「已启用」。也可直接修改注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon`，新建 DWORD 值 `DontDisplayLastUserName` 并设为 `1`。在 Windows Server 2003 及之后版本中此功能已默认启用，无需额外配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1353","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0592","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0592.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6cjr-f6hr-x67r/GHSA-6cjr-f6hr-x67r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86254/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0869.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0868","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1017","title":"Seattle Labs Emurl 邮件附件脚本执行漏洞","description":"Seattle Labs Emurl 2.0 及更早版本存在不安全存储漏洞，程序将电子邮件附件存入启用了脚本执行的目录中，攻击者可通过发送包含恶意 ASP 文件附件的邮件触发该漏洞，当收件人打开邮件时 ASP 脚本自动执行，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Seattle Labs Emurl 系列邮件客户端，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1017"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.843","remediation":"在邮件附件存储目录中禁用脚本执行权限，将附件保存目录移出 Web 根目录或在该目录的 IIS 配置中移除 ASP/脚本映射。升级到 Emurl 2.0 以上版本，并配置附件目录无执行权限。如无法升级，可在 IIS 中将附件目录设置为禁止脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93316253431588&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/544","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1017","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1017.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/544/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0866","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1016","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer HTML Form Control 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 及 FrontPage Express、Outlook Express 5、Eudora 等软件所使用的 HTML Form Control 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造包含超大表单输入字段（如表格单元格中的大量文本框）的恶意网页或 HTML 邮件，诱使用户访问后导致目标系统 CPU 占用率高达 100%，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需认证即可触发，影响范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1016"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.717","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本可修复此漏洞。对于仍使用旧版 IE 的环境，建议禁用 Active Scripting 及在 Outlook Express 中阻止 HTML 邮件加载表单控件。现网用户应迁移至受支持的现代浏览器（如 Edge、Chrome）以免受此及其他已知漏洞影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93578772920970&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/606","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19471","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1016.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1016","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-33jr-59q9-j8vq/GHSA-33jr-59q9-j8vq.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_nt_ms02-005.nasl","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1016.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0865","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0591","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 事件日志权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 事件日志存在不恰当的访问权限配置漏洞，本地普通用户可能能够读取或清除安全事件日志记录。攻击者可利用此漏洞获取系统敏感信息，或在入侵后清理日志痕迹以规避检测。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0591"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.650","remediation":"限制 %SystemRoot%\\System32\\config\\ 目录下 AppEvent.evt、SecEvent.evt、SysEvent.evt 文件的访问权限，仅允许 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 组读取。升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以彻底修复权限配置问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0864","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1014","title":"Sun Solaris mail 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 操作系统的 /usr/bin/mail 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户向 mail 命令的 -m 参数传递超长字符串时，程序未对输入长度进行正确边界检查，导致栈缓冲区溢出。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞精心构造恶意载荷覆盖栈中返回地址，从而以 mail 命令的权限（通常为 root 或 mail 组权限）执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.7 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统账号方能利用，无需网络远程访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1014"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.477","remediation":"安装 Sun 当时发布的补丁 106827-01（SPARC）/ 106828-01（x86），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。对于仍运行 Solaris 7 的遗留系统，可移除 /usr/bin/mail 的 setuid root 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/mail）作为临时缓解，但会影响普通用户使用 mail 命令。现代系统建议迁移至受支持的 Solaris 11 或替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93727925026476&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93846422810162&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/672","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3297","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19529","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1014","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0864.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0863","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0863.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1013","title":"IBM AIX named-xfer 文件覆盖本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 4.1.5 及 4.2.1 版本中的 named-xfer 工具存在文件覆盖漏洞。系统组成员（system group）可通过向 named-xfer 传递 `-f` 参数配合特制的畸形 zone 文件，覆盖系统关键文件，从而将权限提升至 root。攻击者只需具备 system 组权限即可利用，无需认证，危害较大。IBM 未提供官方补丁，建议禁用或限制 named-xfer 的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1013"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.357","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.3.3 或更高版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 (IX86565)。如无法升级，移除 named-xfer 的 setuid root 权限 (chmod u-s /usr/sbin/named-xfer)，并将系统组成员审查清理，确保只有可信任用户属于 system 组。同时限制 named-xfer -f 参数的使用，通过文件权限控制 zone 文件仅允许 root 写入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837026726954&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/673","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1013","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1013.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-958c-wvqf-f46f/GHSA-958c-wvqf-f46f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/673/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0863.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0862","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0589","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表权限漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中关键注册表项存在权限配置不当漏洞，攻击者利用不安全的注册表权限可修改系统关键配置，进而实现本地权限提升或完全控制系统。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限或通过远程获取写入权限后进行利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0589"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.410","remediation":"使用 regedt32.exe 检查并收紧系统关键注册表项（如 HKLM\\SAM、HKLM\\SECURITY、HKLM\\SYSTEM）的 ACL 权限，确保仅 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 拥有完全控制权，移除 Everyone 组的写入权限。同时安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总更新，并在域环境中通过组策略统一加固注册表权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0861","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0861.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1012","title":"Lotus Domino SMTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lotus Domino 4.6.1 的 SMTP 组件在处理超长字符串时存在未正确边界检查的漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器的 SMTP 端口发送特制超长字符串，触发缓冲区溢出或异常处理错误，导致邮件服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AS/400 平台的 Lotus Domino 4.6.1 版本并可能波及其他操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1012"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.237","remediation":"升级 Lotus Domino 至 4.6.2 或更高版本，该版本在 SMTP 服务中增加了输入长度校验，防止超长字符串导致缓冲区崩溃。如使用更现代的版本，建议迁移至 HCL Domino 12.x 或 14.x 长期支持版。同时可在 SMTP 网关或防火墙层面配置最大行长度限制（如 RFC 2821 建议的 998 字符），作为额外深度防御措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13527","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/173","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1012","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/dcc6735c9c3e50e93de820fa1ac9c54ecf6b2577/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0861.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0860","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0860.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0588","title":"OpenSource Router 分片数据包过滤绕过漏洞","description":"路由器或防火墙的包过滤规则未能正确处理异常的 IP 分片数据包，导致攻击者可通过发送特制的分片包绕过访问控制列表或入侵检测系统。该漏洞允许未经认证的远程攻击者绕过安全策略，可能导致信息泄露或服务不可用，影响运行各类开源路由软件及防火墙系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0588"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.290","remediation":"在路由器或防火墙上启用分片包重组与深度检测功能，设置最小分片大小限制，丢弃异常的微小分片包。配置访问控制列表（ACL）对分片包进行精确过滤，防止攻击者利用分片绕过安全策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0588","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0588","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0588.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-56r4-8x77-7j27/GHSA-56r4-8x77-7j27.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0860.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0859","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0587","title":"OpenSource 应用 WWW 服务器文件系统限制绕过漏洞","description":"WWW 服务器未运行在受限文件系统环境中（如未使用 chroot 机制隔离），导致远程攻击者可通过 HTTP 请求直接访问服务器系统关键文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响未正确配置 chroot 环境的各类 WWW 服务器软件，攻击者无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。修复方式为使用 chroot 或容器技术限制 Web 服务的文件系统访问范围。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0587"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.170","remediation":"将 WWW 服务器配置为在 chroot 环境或容器中运行，限制其对 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow 等系统关键文件的访问。修改 Web 服务器配置文件，设置 DocumentRoot 为独立目录，并禁止符号链接跟随 (FollowSymLinks)，同时使用最小权限原则运行服务进程（如 www-data 用户）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0587.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w7xx-5rj3-rrrc/GHSA-w7xx-5rj3-rrrc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0858","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1010","title":"OpenSSH 1.2.27 不允许的 none 加密算法绕过漏洞","description":"SSH 1.2.27 服务器存在安全策略绕过漏洞。攻击者在 SSH 连接协商阶段可强制请求使用 \"none\" 加密算法，即使服务器端策略禁止无加密连接，服务器仍会接受该请求并建立未加密会话。远程攻击者无需任何认证即可利用此漏洞，绕过服务器的安全加密策略，获取明文传输的敏感数据或对通信内容进行中间人攻击。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1010"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.990","remediation":"升级 OpenSSH 至 2.1 或更高版本，SSH1 协议存在此设计缺陷，建议完全禁用 SSH1 协议并仅使用 SSH2。在 sshd_config 中设置 Protocol 2 并添加 Ciphers aes256-ctr,aes192-ctr,aes128-ctr 限制加密算法。如无法升级，在 sshd_config 中显式设置 Ciphers !none 禁用无加密连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94519142415338&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1010","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv.json","https://github.com/phx/cvescan/blob/d8d463e490d1d2d785179e8ace7ff59c2ea15f1f/README.md","https://github.com/privy-cafe/DollarLinuxClub/blob/57ae5d72b23dd6fe9fc5fca4dd120ffdf9dca123/misc/efnetretards.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0857","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0857.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1009","title":"Disney Go Express Search 远程信息访问与修改漏洞","description":"Disney Go Express Search 存在信息泄露与未授权访问漏洞。该软件在用户系统上运行 HTTP 服务器，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络连接访问该服务，窃取或篡改用户的搜索信息。攻击者利用此漏洞可获取用户搜索记录等敏感数据，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。受影响用户需关闭该服务或采取防火墙规则限制外部访问。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1009"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.870","remediation":"立即卸载 Disney Go Express Search 程序，该软件已停止维护且不再有安全更新。可通过 Windows 的\"添加/删除程序\"功能进行卸载。卸载后检查系统是否有残留的 HTTP 服务进程，确保端口未被非法占用。临时缓解措施可在防火墙中阻止该程序的所有入站连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1009","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1009","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1009.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gg88-hgcr-39f4/GHSA-gg88-hgcr-39f4.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olba